    <string name="dialog_help_title">Help</string>
    <string name="dialog_help_content">How PIN entry works:\n\n1. Tap \"Record PIN\" (or Volume Up key)\n2. Speak the PIN clearly (e.g. \"one two three four\")\n3. Optionally copy the result to clipboard\n\nTips:\n• Speak clearly and not too fast\n• Record in a quiet environment\n• Adjust recording duration if needed\n\nVolume Keys:\n• Volume Up: Start recording\n• Volume Down: Cancel active recording\n\nAccessibility:\n• All features work with TalkBack\n• Hardware keys also work with TalkBack\n\nPrivacy:\n• All data is processed locally\n• No internet connection required</string>
